sticking at one thing.

778
01:02:23.332 --> 01:02:28.511
I like to think I'm a multi-player
who can do many things at once.

779
01:02:29.471 --> 01:02:32.214
What's your motivation
for applying for Gangsu Foods?

780
01:02:33.399 --> 01:02:36.968
I had to prove that I wasn't a coward.

781
01:02:37.556 --> 01:02:40.430
Not to anyone else, but myself.

782
01:02:42.790 --> 01:02:44.507
You're a coward.

783
01:02:49.205 --> 01:02:51.435
I've done that now.

784
01:02:51.435 --> 01:02:53.643
Coming this far was enough.

785
01:02:53.643 --> 01:02:56.051
Do you have any last words
you want to say?

786
01:02:57.118 --> 01:02:59.207
Do not choose me.

787
01:03:02.384 --> 01:03:05.388
I will not be an intern here.

788
01:03:12.879 --> 01:03:14.716
Why are you being so stubborn?

789
01:03:14.716 --> 01:03:15.770
About what?

790
01:03:15.770 --> 01:03:18.739
You got notice that you passed,
so why didn't you go into work?

791
01:03:18.739 --> 01:03:21.103
Why did you go back there?

792
01:03:21.788 --> 01:03:24.326
I told you that I think
full-time work is silly.

793
01:03:24.326 --> 01:03:27.147
And working as
a contract cleaner is okay?

794
01:03:27.147 --> 01:03:30.647
I'm different than the others.
I'm only a part-time contract worker.

795
01:03:30.647 --> 01:03:33.049
It's just about freedom. That's all...

796
01:03:33.049 --> 01:03:36.198
I can leave whenever I want.

797
01:03:37.180 --> 01:03:40.962
How sincere are you?

798
01:03:41.498 --> 01:03:43.897
- What do you mean?
- With Hyuk.

799
01:03:43.897 --> 01:03:47.303
I'm asking if you're interested in him
as more than a friend.

800
01:03:49.020 --> 01:03:53.497
Why do I have to tell you that?

801
01:03:54.980 --> 01:03:56.772
Because it bothers me.

802
01:03:57.837 --> 01:03:59.239
Why?

803
01:03:59.774 --> 01:04:02.009
Why would it bother you?

804
01:04:08.997 --> 01:04:11.984
Did you forget?
I'm in charge of looking after Hyuk.

805
01:04:11.984 --> 01:04:14.792
I should know what the people
around Hyuk are thinking.

806
01:04:14.792 --> 01:04:19.335
So, you need to know
my feelings on Hyuk too?

807
01:04:19.335 --> 01:04:20.951
Is that it?

808
01:04:21.980 --> 01:04:24.006
Answer me.

809
01:04:24.006 --> 01:04:27.484
Do you... like Hyuk?

810
01:04:27.484 --> 01:04:30.114
<i>Yes, I do like it.</i>

811
01:04:30.114 --> 01:04:33.294
Mix coffee, drip coffee,
espresso. I like it all.

812
01:04:33.294 --> 01:04:36.114
Oh, really? Then go make some.

813
01:04:36.114 --> 01:04:38.085
- Me?
- Yes, you.

814
01:04:38.085 --> 01:04:40.674
The intern should go.
Should I do it, then?

815
01:04:40.674 --> 01:04:42.596
Yes, I will.

816
01:05:04.178 --> 01:05:07.024
Here you go. Recharge yourself.

817
01:05:09.151 --> 01:05:11.540
- Oh, Byun Hyuk.
- Yes?

818
01:05:11.540 --> 01:05:14.160
This is one of the companies
we work with.

819
01:05:14.160 --> 01:05:15.960
Get them to stamp this with their seal.

820
01:05:15.960 --> 01:05:17.100
I should do it?

821
01:05:17.100 --> 01:05:19.951
Yes, it's not hard at all.
Just get them to stamp it.

822
01:05:19.951 --> 01:05:23.460
Think of it as
your first job as the intern.

823
01:05:23.460 --> 01:05:24.750
You can do a good job, right?

824
01:05:24.750 --> 01:05:27.910
Of course. I can do a good job.

825
01:05:27.910 --> 01:05:29.308
Take a look here.

826
01:05:29.308 --> 01:05:33.218
Here, here, and here.

827
01:05:33.218 --> 01:05:35.415
Get them to stamp it
with their legal seal.

828
01:05:36.618 --> 01:05:39.292
- You know what that is, right?
- Yes.

829
01:05:42.027 --> 01:05:43.547
I'll succeed and return.

830
01:05:43.547 --> 01:05:47.113
So, the factory is
in Gyeonggi-do, Anseong?

831
01:05:47.113 --> 01:05:49.460
Get a car from the admin team.

832
01:05:49.460 --> 01:05:51.138
Yes, I will.

833
01:05:57.480 --> 01:05:59.978
This is your first task?

834
01:05:59.978 --> 01:06:02.480
Yes, I just need them
to stamp their seal.

835
01:06:02.480 --> 01:06:05.089
Still, they gave this to an intern?

836
01:06:05.089 --> 01:06:07.529
Yes, I just need to get it stamped.

837
01:06:07.529 --> 01:06:12.330
I just don't think this will be
easy to get resolved on your own.

838
01:06:12.330 --> 01:06:15.464
It's okay. I just
need to get it stamped.

839
01:06:16.728 --> 01:06:18.430
Why are you here anyway?

840
01:06:18.430 --> 01:06:21.190
Could you possibly be
my designated driver?

841
01:06:21.190 --> 01:06:22.390
A driver? Why?

842
01:06:22.390 --> 01:06:26.174
My license is suspended
until the end of the month.

843
01:06:26.174 --> 01:06:27.745
Could you help me?

844
01:06:30.520 --> 01:06:31.772
Answer me.

845
01:06:31.772 --> 01:06:35.062
Do you... like Hyuk?

846
01:06:37.361 --> 01:06:39.805
Okay. 50,000 won, deal?

847
01:06:39.805 --> 01:06:41.301
Deal.

848
01:07:00.569 --> 01:07:02.879
I think this is the right place.

849
01:07:03.892 --> 01:07:05.765
No one's here though.

850
01:07:10.535 --> 01:07:12.094
Joon.

851
01:07:12.094 --> 01:07:14.924
You shouldn't just go in there.

852
01:07:14.924 --> 01:07:16.560
Is anyone here?

853
01:07:16.560 --> 01:07:17.839
Joon...

854
01:07:17.839 --> 01:07:19.725
Excuse me!

855
01:07:27.089 --> 01:07:28.611
Anyone here?

856
01:07:29.417 --> 01:07:31.036
Is no one here?

857
01:07:31.036 --> 01:07:32.245
Joon.

858
01:07:36.343 --> 01:07:37.596
It's open.

859
01:07:42.558 --> 01:07:44.453
Hello.

860
01:07:47.622 --> 01:07:50.902
Is it okay to just go in? Is this okay?

861
01:07:50.902 --> 01:07:52.794
Is no one here?

862
01:08:05.752 --> 01:08:07.319
What's wrong, Joon?

863
01:08:21.480 --> 01:08:28.480
Subtitles by DramaFever

864
01:08:44.629 --> 01:08:48.206
<i>[Revolutionary Love]</i>

865
01:08:48.206 --> 01:08:49.701
<i>She's a strange girl.</i>

866
01:08:49.701 --> 01:08:52.835
<i>She's not someone who would be
hanging around with Byun Hyuk.</i>

867
01:08:52.835 --> 01:08:53.993
<i>Look into Baek Joon.</i>

868
01:08:53.993 --> 01:08:56.203
<i>Find out why she's always with Hyuk.</i>

869
01:08:56.203 --> 01:08:58.614
<i>What are you doing?
Are you looking into my background?</i>

870
01:08:58.614 --> 01:09:00.931
<i>Why am I here? Did you kidnap me?</i>

871
01:09:00.931 --> 01:09:02.917
<i>Negotiate with them and get it.</i>

872
01:09:02.917 --> 01:09:04.245
<i>How can I do that?</i>

873
01:09:04.245 --> 01:09:05.259
<i>How can they do this, Jae Hoon?</i>

874
01:09:05.259 --> 01:09:07.870
<i>Do I have to resolve work issues for you?
Figure it out yourself.</i>

875
01:09:07.870 --> 01:09:09.220
<i>Are you getting other ideas?</i>

876
01:09:09.220 --> 01:09:10.648
<i>Are you feeling bad
for your friend, Hyuk?</i>

877
01:09:10.648 --> 01:09:13.238
<i>I wish you would be
different than typical employees.</i>

878
01:09:13.238 --> 01:09:16.845
<i>If I do become different like you say,
can I be a man to you?</i>

